    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>&quot;It axes and comes backses.&quot;</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boomeraxe is a bullet hell dungeon crawler with a unique core mechanic: Your only weapon hurts you too. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of The G'Knight as you dare to escape the cold reaches of Icestralia—a very real place with even realer consequences.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stuff you <u><i><strong>will</strong></i></u> find here:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blistering action<br>Synergistic powerups<br>Boss battles<br>Meta progression<br>Questionable zoology<br>Costs about as much as a king-size candy bar (tastes worse)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stuff you <u><i><strong>won't</strong></i></u> find here:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backtracking through rooms you've already cleared<br>Obligatory narrative elements<br>Not fun until you have a good build<br>Exorbitant pricing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glory awaits! But so does death. Your call.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With music by Josh Whelchel!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390650/extras/7d7210e3e245a982f619aea9e96d097b.poster.avif?t=1728311628\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390650/extras/7d7210e3e245a982f619aea9e96d097b.webm?t=1728311628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
